<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">周颂·清庙</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson3b27d3d20935">
於穆清庙，肃雍显相。<br />济济多士，秉文之德。<br />对越在天，骏奔走在庙。<br />不显不承，无射于人斯！
</div>
</div>
